cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with cross-modal image synthesis and proposes a novel approach for filter learning. This is a problem that is commonly addressed in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) research. The specific application domain is medical imaging (cs.MM), which is also mentioned in the abstract. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of a closed loop joint filter learning strategy, which suggests the involvement of neural networks (cs.NE).
